There was a snort from LEO PRIME as the mayhem broke out around him.
Retorts against accusations and threats.

"MAXIMALS Stand down!" He said as he saw a possible escalation, his
optics flashing dangerously. No, he was not a TUSCON, but he definitly
did have a temper of his own.

Loking over at DINOBOT his optics bright with his own repressed anger,
"Your commander has told you to lay off and take your place, I would
suggest you do that." He said.

He looked around at the MAXIMALS with him, "You do realize that he is
trying to bait you into breaking the truce right?" His voice was
nearly a growl as he tried to make his point stick. "If you attack him
then the Predacons can break the truce."

"Yeah!" Came a voice from above, it was INJECTOR's voice, one of the
PREDACON fuzors who was just arriving. "Go ahead and fire, I would
love to lay open a few Maximals."

INJECTOR was followed by BUZZCLAW, QUICKSTRIKE and TERRORGATOR, quite
possibly the very troops that SKY SHADOW had been calling a short
while ago, giving them the okay to fly move in.

"I'm ready to kick some kiesters!" QUICKSTRIKE said as he moved in.

BUZZCLAW chuckled, "No, not yet. But if they start something, we can finish it!"

TERRORGATOR just lumbered up, his well armored bulk all the threat he needed.

"Slag, it just get's better and better." LEO said as he watched the
Predacon reinforcement arrive.

(TAG)

Preston
